The paper discusses the performance of different initialization methods for the k-means clustering algorithm, which is a popular machine learning technique used in various application domains. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
